<br>
I know there are going to be some of those who wont like this new "rule" but I can't make everyone happy.. and I'm sorry, I try to do that (make everyone happy).. it's really hard.. but there are sites where people do go to sell in game items for money and people go to them way more for that kind of stuff than here.<br>
<br>
So please, without flaming me, or others.. let's just keep this an ingame items for ingame money only auction board. Thank you<br>
<br>
- Elaylie.<br>
<br>
